ZH: 在冬天，外面的温度非常低，我们要穿厚衣服。
EN: In winter, the temperature outside is very low, so we need to wear thick clothes.

ZH: 这个冷藏库可以保持低温，确保食物新鲜。
EN: This cold storage can maintain a low temperature to ensure the freshness of the food.

ZH: 冬季运动员们经常要在低温环境下进行训练。
EN: Winter athletes often have to train in low-temperature environments.

ZH: 冰箱的低温设置有助于保存食物。
EN: The low temperature setting of the refrigerator helps preserve food.

ZH: 在北极地区，气温非常低，很少有植物能够生长。
EN: In the Arctic region, the temperature is very low, so few plants can grow.

ZH: 低温下，水会结冰变成冰。
EN: Under low temperatures, water will freeze and turn into ice.

ZH: 多穿一点衣服可以帮助你抵抗低温。
EN: Wearing more clothes can help you withstand low temperatures.

ZH: 来到高海拔地区，气温会逐渐变得低温。
EN: When you arrive at high-altitude areas, the temperature will gradually become lower.

ZH: 春天到来之前，气温仍然很低。
EN: The temperature remains low before spring arrives.

ZH: 在低温条件下，许多昆虫会进入休眠状态。
EN: Under low temperature conditions, many insects will enter a dormant state.

ZH: 这款冰箱可以调节到低温模式，适合保存冷冻食品。
EN: This refrigerator can be adjusted to a low-temperature mode, suitable for storing frozen foods.

ZH: 在山区，夜间气温会降到极低温度。
EN: In mountainous areas, the nighttime temperature can drop to extremely low levels.

ZH: 许多动物会在冬季选择躲避低温。
EN: Many animals choose to avoid low temperatures in winter.

ZH: 低温环境下，植物的生长速度会减缓。
EN: Under low temperature conditions, the growth rate of plants will slow down.

ZH: 我们的冷藏室可以保持稳定的低温，以保存蔬菜水果。
EN: Our cold storage room can maintain a stable low temperature to preserve vegetables and fruits.

ZH: 要注意不要长时间暴露在低温环境中，容易导致感冒。
EN: Be careful not to be exposed to low temperatures for a long time, as it can lead to catching a cold.

ZH: 春季来临，气温逐渐升高，摆脱了低温的困扰。
EN: With the arrival of spring, the temperature gradually rises, getting rid of the problem of low temperature.

ZH: 生活在极地地区的动植物已经适应了极低温度。
EN: Plants and animals living in polar regions have adapted to extremely low temperatures.

ZH: 穿上厚重外套能够御寒，抵御低温的侵袭。
EN: Wearing a thick coat can keep you warm and resist the invasion of low temperatures.

ZH: 现代冷冻技术可以在极低温下保存食物长时间不腐坏。
EN: Modern freezing technology can preserve food for a long time without spoilage at extremely low temperatures.
